data.description: Welcome to this beautiful two story home situated on an oversized lot in Sendero. Features include a stone & brick facade, covered front porch, two story entry, formal dining, open-concept living, 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, a large gameroom & screened-in back patio! LVP flooring extends throughout the common areas. The kitchen boasts a walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, breakfast bar & adjoining breakfast room. First floor primary suite with an oversized shower with built-in seat, soaking tub, dual-sink vanity & generous walk-in closet. Upgraded contemporary stair railing. Zoned to Lamar CISD schools & conveniently located with easy access to 59, 99, Brazos Town Center, Sugar Land & more.
